

Day-02 Create your First Database & Tables
===========================================

When we Initially use any Application or Website it asks us to Signup and provide some basic information like (first name, last name, age, phone number, email, address)


- For Single Line Comment we can give below

(# or --)


- For Multi Line Comment we can give below

/*
And between  this we can write the data which we want to comment
*/



-> To Create a Database
- create database retail_db;


-> To Use any Database use below Command
- use retail_db;


-> We are creating  a Orders Table under retail_db Database

- CREATE TABLE orders (
order_id INT,
order_date DATETIME,
customer_id INT,
order_status VARCHAR(30)
);




-> We are creating  a Customers Table under retail_db Database

- CREATE TABLE customers (
customer_id INT,
customer_fname VARCHAR(45) ,
customer_lname VARCHAR(45),
customer_email VARCHAR45) ,
customer_password VARCHAR(45) ,
customer_street VARCHAR255) ,
customer_city VARCHAR45) ,
customer_state VARCHAR(45) ,
customer_zipcode VARCHAR(45)
);






- To Drop a Database we use below Command
- DROP DATABASE retail_db;



- To Drop a Table we use below Command
- DROP TABLE customers;









